facts.seriesTitle: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services (percent)
facts.fact_text: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services declined from 22.1 % in 1990 to 1.9% in 2017.

facts.seriesTitle: Fixed Internet broadband subscriptions (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: Fixed-broadband internet penetration reached 0.1 per 100 inhabitants in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Internet users  (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: The number of Internet users per 100 inhabitants increased from 0.2 in 2000 to 3.9 in 2017.

facts.seriesTitle: Total official development assistance (gross disbursement) for technical cooperation (millions of 2018 dollars)
facts.fact_text: The total gross disbursement of official development assistance for technical cooperation in constant prices of 2018 declined from 21.3 million dollars in 2000 to 13.3 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status declined from 15.0 % in 2005 to 13.0% in 2015.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status was 13.0 % in 2015.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, most-favored nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average most-favored nation status tariff applied by developed countries increased from 2.4 % in 2000 to 2.6% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average preferential status tariff applied by developed countries declined from 0.7 % in 2000 to 0.3% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Dollar value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries (dollars)
facts.fact_text: The value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries was 148492.2 dollars in 2017.
